<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Dread Forged Shield Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
Submitted by: Spiderinx<BR>
<BR>
Talk to Nivold Predd in Paineel and ask him about the summoning of the dread.<BR>
<BR>
He will tell you he needs some items:<BR>
1) Eye of Griffon<BR>
2) Powder of Reanimation<BR>
3) Brain of Ishva Mal (Splitpaw)<BR>
4) Ice Giant toes  (Everfrost)<BR>
<BR>
He also tells you that the place to get the powder of reanimation is from a necro residing now in Unrest, and that you must give this necro (named Khrix) a fire beetle eye.  With that, Khrix will summon an undead creature, which is a 40 level ghoul who spawns in the closed room directly behind Khrix and next to the Magi room.  You must kill the ghoul who will have the powder of reanimation.</div>
<BR>
