<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Raincrow</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-22 15:16:52</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>if the faction you need is with the Heretics then kill erud guards, erud emissaries, ToxHighEmissaries, and any wandering Mage, Wiz, or Enc NPCs.  Just don't kill the wandering necros or Heretics.  I am a shaman and my alchemy components and Books are in Paineel, so down with Erudin :)  The guards hit harder than they con and heal too!  I 38 barb shaman and was with a 35 DE necro, we were camping them, They hit damn hard and fast.  Once you break up the spawn it should be under control.<BR>
<BR>
Faction for Killing the guards are as follows:<BR>
Heretics Better<BR>
Erud Counsil Worse<BR>
Kerraians Better<BR>
Erud Guards Worse<BR>
and one other worse, another Tox Erud faction.<BR>
<BR>
Killing does not affect Qeynos or anywhere else :)</font></td></tr></table>
